Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ones who shrunk my body, the Black Organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With each move I've made toward grasping the Organization's weakness thus far...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI has been a figure that supported me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:14.41,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Gin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:14.41,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Akai Suuichi\NFBI
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The covert plan underlying our strategy to bring an end to the Organization remains undiscovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:18.95,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Vermouth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:22.37,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mizunashi Rena / Hondou Hidemi\NCIA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the condition that her brother Eisuke was admitted to the Witness Protection program...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizunashi Rena agreed to return to the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Several days later, when we went to a hotel buffet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got involved in the murder case of the president of Foreign Talent Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whereupon one of the suspects turned out to be the FBI agent Camel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:48.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,James Black
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:48.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Jodie Starling\NFBI
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Jodie...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:58.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Running in the darkness —\ha red scream and a black shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Undercover in the Organization, Mizunashi Rena is given the command to rub out Akai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan is brought to you by these sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:03:01.91,Title,,0,0,0,,CLASH OF RED AND BLACK\NINNOCENCE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:10.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This evil looking man is with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:17.67,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Andre Camel (27)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when they're considering agents for the Bureau...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-They don't judge them by their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why is he here in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know that I messed up a job for the FBI and came to Japan to console myself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I took so long to come back, he got worried about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:41.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, Andre Camel is my lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so? Why are you still in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think her Japanese is getting a bit better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before, she was saying things like, "sou desssu."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's because I've been taking a crash course from Andre, who's really good at Japanese, that I've improved so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And both of us have just found it difficult to leave Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:22.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, that's exactly right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason, that seems a bit contrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, even if he is with the FBI, that doesn't exclude him as a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need you to stay until you're cleared of suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, for letting me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the FBI pulls out of the hospital, I want to see you all once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found this paper bag in the tool storage area in the rooftop restaurant plaza restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside was a raincoat, gloves, and a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These may have been used by the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means we probably won't find any gunpowder when we examine these three suspects clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, if they had disposed of the clothes they used for the crime, the culprit could have forced their way into the crowded elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit took the stairs to the roof and went into the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then put their gloves, clothing, and gun in a paper bag and hid it in the tool storage area, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means at least five minutes would have passed before they were done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would have looked suspicious if they did all of that in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They also probably wouldn't have expected the police to arrive this quickly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, we also checked the video from the security cameras in the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were no foreigners on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about Asian foreigners?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't know from their appearance, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:06:03.13,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Irina Palmer (24)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:06:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do not think the president employed any Asian people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president always said:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A person who doesn't look Japanese at all and yet speaks Japanese is interesting."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the suspicious ones are still those three people there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, the most suspicious person...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would be the one who was hiding in the restroom, Hal{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:25.82,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hal Buckner (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already said I wasn't hiding, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you normally avoid hiding in the same restroom where you hid that kind of stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:38.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you say the investigators and officers coming, you could have gone back in there to hide without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's also possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, the coat is fitted for slender men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The length would exactly match Toby{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.47,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Toby Keynes (27)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With something that size, this FBI guy could force himself into it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, it's not just us three men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The secretary could have worn it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As they say, "better too big than too small."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She could have been lying up to now in order to deceive us over her own crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we need to consider that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She may have worn a man's coat to make it seem like a man was responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, it seems certain that one of you four were responsible for making the president eat those bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe, other than the bullets, the president really was eating something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, look here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the president's right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it look like he was holding something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, it does seem that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no food on top of the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like he was eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like he was holding something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That pen on the desk or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only a small amount, but there are traces of blood on the shaft of the pen and on the memo paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are also slight traces of writing on the memo paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could the president have written something before he died?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the culprit took it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, have a blood analysis performed and determine what was written.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, confirm it was the president's handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how we would investigate it, right, Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the blood on the memo paper belonged to President Sunouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and they say the writing on the memo was his as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? What was on the memo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's written in English so I'm not sure what it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or even if it's a dying message.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring my tux.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring my tux?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watashi no tuxedo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...tottekiitte kure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Continuing with this job is becoming mentally stressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If possible, I want to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the human resources manager at the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told them clearly that I couldn't be an announcer any longer and needed to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's troublesome to have them ineptly searching for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, the Organization can hear every word I speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:24.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are all sorts of bugs and transmitters on me right now and always two or three guards watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That person{\i0} that even now continues to suspect me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has a mission for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to relay an order from {\i1}that person{\i0} that suspects so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You will eliminate someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To prove you can be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eliminate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI agent...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai Shuuichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuuichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI agent, Akai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been mulling over how suspicious it was, {\i1}that person{\i0} and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How extremely easy it was to recover you from the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the plan is to have you kill the FBI's trump card, Akai Shuuichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And have you prove your innocence to us personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Kir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you've got some reason preventing you from doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do I need a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin, how can I approach Akai when even you don't know how to handle him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I approach them poorly, they'll capture me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't approach him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You will only lure him into our firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:26.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You returned to the Organization just fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But are now being treated like a black sheep due to your mistake and capture at the hands of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you no longer have a place here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to leave us and flee to a foreign country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say all that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:42.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, you will deal only with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you offer some sort of rewarding information, he'll definitely bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when he comes in blindly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all will come forward and shoot him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll handle that on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His nose is surprisingly sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he detects our presence, he'll see through the trap and turn his heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be letting us observe the course of events from a location where his bullets cannot reach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll place a bug on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And of course, a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do as you've asked, but can you give me a little time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll call him now, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you fail to, you'll be calling the Grim Reaper instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:42.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not even sure the FBI will want to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is a possibility, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the intel from our guy, they're still holding up in that hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now, one of their agents has somehow become involved in a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI's eyes are all focused on him for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We cannot miss this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A case?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some company president found himself with extra airholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just your usual murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Bring my tuxedo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what was written on the memo the president left?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Bring my tux."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Bring" is "to get"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And "tux" is short for "tuxedo".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pen and paper both have the president's blood on them, and it's in his handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more, there's the memo paper that was torn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:45.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stricken president wrote it as he was dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the culprit noticed it and took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be a "daiingu messeeji"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dying message!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of you are English teachers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's true that I teach English at a cram school, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't these people FBI agents?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For various reasons, I was teaching for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's right, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:22.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, secretary Irina{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you happen to know what he meant by "bring my tuxedo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was a message from the president to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was going to a party tonight, so he asked me to bring his tuxedo by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it's just a regular memo that has nothing to do with the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president said he was going out this afternoon for a meal with an up and coming talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:55.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was for when I returned while he was out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:16:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you're the one who tore out the memo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I saw the president was dead, I called right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did not touch anything until the policemen came!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I did know about the tuxedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left a message about it on the answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answering machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Palmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you already out, President sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found the file you asked for and am bringing it there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll get the tuxedo for the party tonight later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friday, 1:27 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the culprit heard this and hurried away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe the culprit recorded it after the crime to make us think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's at least possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If "Bring my tux" has some sort of hidden meaning in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She may have purposely mentioned the tuxedo in the message in order to deceive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you mention a tuxedo, the one who that points to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be this man, who was working as a model, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the work we models usually do, wearing all sorts of clothes stylishly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not just tuxedos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president was going to wear one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, in any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be investigating in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone please go wait in the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi, you figured out something about the memo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president could have added something to a previous memo to make it a dying message, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that were the case, forensics should have noticed the additional writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anything to add or remove from these English letters to change the meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, I'm not sure this is the best time to ask, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said just the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That you came to Japan two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu was still undercover in the Organization then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you must have heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About our failure to capture an executive member of theirs due to an agent's mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The agent who made that mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had arranged to meet that executive in a warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While we were all lying in wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lone old man appeared and sat down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was ignoring him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for me, without thinking, I yelled:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You should get out of here, it's dangerous!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:19:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the old man you drove away was one of their members checking on the arrangement?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to that, the executive never showed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they discovered that Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was with the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some undercover investigation had failed and there was an agent who returned to the office with his head held in shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, when Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} asked if anyone was up for the plan this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can handle the driving job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'll come to Japan right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He warned me that I could die, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mistake was the cause of his girlfriend's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told me not to worry about it, that his girlfriend had been aware of the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,FBI?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll be putting an end to it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're trying to fool me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think of something better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't be surprised at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you knew, why didn't you leave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew I was just using you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you not tell without asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your phone has been ringing for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizunashi Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it OK to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is anyone around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:20:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're surprised, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I contacted you so soon after returning to the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Explain what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's become difficult to stay in the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want your help to leave and fly out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'll offer any information that the FBI wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we meet now, just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't be a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long as you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll mail you the time and place after this call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today is Friday the 13th.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have believed earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That his fate would be sealed on such an appropriate day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was Mizunashi Rena on the phone, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She asked if we could meet now in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A private meeting with her could be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be more prudent not to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, except...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it is a trap and I do not show, in 7 or 8 cases out of 9, she'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm confident my sixth sense will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She may just be CIA...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I believe she has a clever plan to get out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-At any rate, I'll call Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} so we FBI can...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.53,0:22:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The message left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.46,0:24:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The summoning call.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do they imply a trap or a cry for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.55,0:24:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we take a risk by going on the offensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we jump in?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A glimpse of the unexpected truth hidden behind their evil ways is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Detective Conan...
